    author: "By The Olsen Tribune",
    headline: "Crude's Wild Ride: Energy Traders Brace for Prolonged Middle East Premium",
    deck: "Oil markets are swinging on every headline from the Gulf, forcing institutional investors to rethink hedging strategies as geopolitical risk becomes the dominant price driver.",
