    headline: "Iran Conflict Sends Shockwaves Through Energy Markets, Upending Central Bank Calculus",
    deck: "As crude prices swing on ceasefire headlines, policymakers from London to Beijing are confronting a fresh inflation shock that threatens to derail fragile recoveries.",
